Package: subpca
Title: Clustered and Hierarchical Principal Components Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Bradley",
           family = "Buchsbaum",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Provides PCA workflows that decompose data by feature clusters,
    combine block-wise decompositions with a meta-PCA, and extend to
    hierarchical and time-contrast settings. Includes projection,
    reconstruction, and diagnostics for multi-stage PCA models.
